---
title: Loaded Chorizo Chilli Sweet Potato Jacky-P   with Bean Chilli and Cheese
description: Jacket potatoes aren't just for baked beans and cheese. Our Loaded Sweet Potato Jacky-P is topped with a veggie bean chilli as a twist on the humble jacket potato for a comforting weeknight dinner.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R21_W07_UK_V12824-3_Main_2_low-51e91de1.jpg
